[
  {
    "startTime": 80,
    "endTime": 4400,
    "duration": 4320,
    "text": "We are continuing our Black History"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2000,
    "endTime": 6799,
    "duration": 4799,
    "text": "Month celebration of people who show us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4400,
    "endTime": 8960,
    "duration": 4560,
    "text": "the power of community, like activist"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6799,
    "endTime": 11920,
    "duration": 5121,
    "text": "Shirley Reigns, better known as Miss"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8960,
    "endTime": 14960,
    "duration": 6000,
    "text": "Shirley, who devoted her life to seeing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11920,
    "endTime": 18000,
    "duration": 6080,
    "text": "the beauty in others. Her activism began"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14960,
    "endTime": 20800,
    "duration": 5840,
    "text": "as a way to heal her own trauma from"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18000,
    "endTime": 23519,
    "duration": 5519,
    "text": "losing her two-year-old son, but quickly"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20800,
    "endTime": 25920,
    "duration": 5120,
    "text": "turned into a viral movement. Miss"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23519,
    "endTime": 28960,
    "duration": 5441,
    "text": "Shirley's mission focused on providing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25920,
    "endTime": 31760,
    "duration": 5840,
    "text": "the unhoused in LA Skid Row with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28960,
    "endTime": 35200,
    "duration": 6240,
    "text": "self-worth restoring services. Her"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31760,
    "endTime": 38399,
    "duration": 6639,
    "text": "nonprofit beauty to the streets, offered"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35200,
    "endTime": 41600,
    "duration": 6400,
    "text": "food, hygiene, beauty services, and what"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38399,
    "endTime": 43600,
    "duration": 5201,
    "text": "she called spiritual CPR to the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41600,
    "endTime": 45840,
    "duration": 4240,
    "text": "community. She even learned sign"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43600,
    "endTime": 48320,
    "duration": 4720,
    "text": "language to communicate with some of the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45840,
    "endTime": 51680,
    "duration": 5840,
    "text": "hearing impaired. When needs of the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48320,
    "endTime": 54559,
    "duration": 6239,
    "text": "unhoused increased after the pandemic,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51680,
    "endTime": 58079,
    "duration": 6399,
    "text": "Miss Shirley went viral on social media,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54559,
    "endTime": 60480,
    "duration": 5921,
    "text": "gathering donations. She gained 7"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58079,
    "endTime": 63120,
    "duration": 5041,
    "text": "million followers who helped her feed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60480,
    "endTime": 65680,
    "duration": 5200,
    "text": "thousands and expanded operations to San"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63120,
    "endTime": 68400,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "Diego, Las Vegas, and Long Beach,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65680,
    "endTime": 70960,
    "duration": 5280,
    "text": "California. She showed the world that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68400,
    "endTime": 74159,
    "duration": 5759,
    "text": "this community was like all of us with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70960,
    "endTime": 76720,
    "duration": 5760,
    "text": "kids, families, many with jobs, but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74159,
    "endTime": 80000,
    "duration": 5841,
    "text": "without a home. She was honored with an"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76720,
    "endTime": 83200,
    "duration": 6480,
    "text": "NAACP Image Award and one of CNN's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80000,
