    "duration": 6720,
    "text": "heroes of the year in 2021."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83200,
    "endTime": 88960,
    "duration": 5760,
    "text": "Miss Shirley passed away last month."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86720,
    "endTime": 92240,
    "duration": 5520,
    "text": ">> She was 58 years old,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88960,
    "endTime": 94159,
    "duration": 5199,
    "text": ">> but her legacy proves that the power of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92240,
    "endTime": 97479,
    "duration": 5239,
    "text": "compassion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94159,
